{"tid":792493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【安泰邪邨】男子安泰邨天橋墮下　遺下一地血跡　當場死亡","createTime":"2018-08-24T14:58:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T15:16:20.000Z","uid":50162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0705372b2f73948350d986a1f2186aae7759e379","tid":792493,"uid":50162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T14:58:36.000Z","msg":"今日下午4時許，秀茂坪安泰邨連接順天邨的天橋有人從高處墮下，當場死亡。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息指，一名年約30-40歲的男子，在該天橋升降機塔約6-7樓的梯間位置一躍而下，20歲姓鄺途人發現報警。救護員接報到場，證實男子當場死亡，現場遺下一地血跡。警方於現場沒有檢獲遺書，初步調查顯示事件沒有可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<br />\n高達14層的安泰邨天橋一向備受關注，由於安泰邨位於山上，居民到附近的順天邨時，必需使用天橋，有網民曾笑稱可活用這條升降機塔行樓梯做運動。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1520311/org/c67ef93fbb0b33764f1aa6a32bd913ac.jpg/o0mV1cnG8tWHfKh3mzBAbgsihiiojwRRuhsV5robFeY?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1520311%2Forg%2Fc67ef93fbb0b33764f1aa6a32bd913ac.jpg%2Fo0mV1cnG8tWHfKh3mzBAbgsihiiojwRRuhsV5robFeY%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=4109942b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1520698/org/f3b473601b41b7817f2cfbef23810bbf.jpg/0cDLusJvaGa_9NqMEeUjEhsvdgVkzi2LeGlr_nhpa_4?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1520698%2Forg%2Ff3b473601b41b7817f2cfbef23810bbf.jpg%2F0cDLusJvaGa_9NqMEeUjEhsvdgVkzi2LeGlr_nhpa_4%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=29693ff2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男子當場死亡。（林振華攝）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1520350/org/2022424d29417b29f1d1fed21ae534a0.jpg/iM1LHD_KxnDynqBa8FsF4Xz9Ib6UvrYm3aNXht2jV4Y?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1520350%2Forg%2F2022424d29417b29f1d1fed21ae534a0.jpg%2FiM1LHD_KxnDynqBa8FsF4Xz9Ib6UvrYm3aNXht2jV4Y%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=65431bd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男子當場死亡，現場遺下一地血跡。（林振華攝）<br />\n<br />\n新聞來源：<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/突發/196895/男子安泰邨天橋墮下-遺下一地血跡-當場死亡\" data-sr-url=\"htt